<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>
    <hr>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <%= image_tag "IMG_2280.JPG", width: "300",alt: "profile image", class: 'profile-img' %>
    <div class="skills">
      <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
      <div class="skill">
        <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
        <div class="progress">
          <div
            class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
            role ="progressbar"
            aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
            aria-valuemax="100"
            style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
          ></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

    <div class="col-md-8">

    <p>Short loin capicola alcatra cupim, pork belly pork loin salami turkey cow tongue doner corned beef ham hamburger. Chicken tail doner jowl, tongue ham hock tri-tip biltong picanha bacon pork chop flank pork loin. Jowl pastrami alcatra tenderloin. Pork belly brisket pork loin tenderloin t-bone andouille ham hock meatloaf alcatra chuck pastrami porchetta doner short ribs. Jowl fatback pork belly shoulder rump pork. Pork loin pork chop ham turkey swine short ribs pig leberkas strip steak jowl pork belly sausage.</p>

